account.descriptionLink:
Let's kick off the formal NoGoal DAO with a first proposal to incentivize people to learn more about how DAOs can work on Solana and get involved with ours.

I suggest airdropping 50k INO (~7$USD) to all members who deposited INO to vote on this proposal.

Limits: 5M budget, so first 100 DAO members - Only the addresses that holded INO before Dec 23 are eligible, to avoid fake alt addresses.
account.name: Reward first DAO members with a 50k INO airdrop
